a,b,c
a^3 + 4b^3 + c^3 = 3b(a^2 + c^2)
a+c=2b
a^3+4b^3+c^3
=(a+c)^3-3ac(a+c)+4b^3
=8b^3-6abc+4b^3
=3b(4b^2-2ac)
=3b((a+c)^2-2ac)
=3b(a^2+c^2)
a=b-x
c=b+x
x
(s+t)^3 = s^3 + 3s^2t + 3st^2 + t^3
(s+t)^2 = s^2 + 2st + t^2
a = (b-x),  c=(b+x)
a^{3}+4b^{3}+c^{3} = (b-x)^3+4b^3+(b+x)^3
 \Rightarrow (b-x)^{3}+4b^{3}+(b+x)^3 =  6b^{3}+6bx^{2}
